          <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">Does Webority provide multi-vendor and multi-platform interoperability?</button>
          <div class="faq-a"><p>We build on open standards (OpenAPI, OAuth 2.0, FHIR where relevant) and integrate with India Stack components (Aadhaar, DigiLocker, UMANG, ServicePlus, BharatKosh, PFMS) and existing departmental ERPs.</p></div>
